{
  "texts": [
    "Therefore, understanding student-AI interaction patterns can be helpful for integrating AI in educational contexts effectively by meeting individual learning styles and needs (Wang et al., 2023).",
    "Despite the growing literature on the potential of LLM-based chatbots like Chat-GPT in programming education, there remains a significant gap in understanding how to best integrate these tools to enhance learning experiences and outcomes.",
    "There is limited research on how different AI integration approaches can lead to distinct interaction profiles among students, and the impact of students' interactions with ChatGPT on their performance.",
    "In this context, the aim of this study is to investigate the interactions between students and ChatGPT during programming learning by analyzing the effects of different instructional interventions for ChatGPT integration on student learning and experiences.",
    "The findings of this study are anticipated to significantly enhance the expanding body of knowledge on the integration of gen-AI tools in educational settings."
  ]
}